</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Sklop hidrauličkog uređaja/upravljačkog modula ESP<sup>®</sup>-a je zamijenjen.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<ptxt>
Izvršite kalibriranje senzora prema uputama pod naslovom 
<intxref refid = "AHRAP70A4606002">Kalibriranje senzora</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
